      • toEpochMilli

        public static long toEpochMilli(LocalDateTime time)
        Converts a LocalDateTime object and converts it to respective milliseconds since Unix Epoch. The assumed time zone is UTC.
        Parameters:
        time - time value to be converted to milliseconds since Unix Epoch.
        Returns:
        Representation of the the provided time stamp in milliseconds since Unix Epoch.

      • toLocalDateTime

        public static LocalDateTime toLocalDateTime(long epochMillis)
        Converts a unix timestamp as a long to a LocalDateTime object. The assumed time zone is UTC.
        Parameters:
        epochMillis - time value as long in milliseconds since Unix epoch.
        Returns:
        Representation of the provided time stamp as LocalDateTime object in UTC time zone.
